<div class="comment" id="comment8887">
  <p class="banner"><a href="/web/20100628135048/http://ja.doukaku.org/user/380/" target="_top">vtwntmtn</a><a href="/web/20100628135048/http://ja.doukaku.org/qa/#medal" target="_top"><img src="/web/20100628135048im_/http://ja.doukaku.org/static/image/star_silver.png" border=0/></a><a href="/web/20100628135048/http://ja.doukaku.org/qa/#anomark" target="_top"><img src="/web/20100628135048im_/http://ja.doukaku.org/static/image/anomark.png" border=0/></a>

	
	&nbsp;
	<a href="/web/20100628135048/http://ja.doukaku.org/comment/8887/">#8887</a>(<script language="JavaScript">print_time(new Date("2009/05/04 07:59 GMT"));</script><noscript>2009/05/04 07:59 GMT</noscript>)
	
	
	
	[<a href="/web/20100628135048/http://ja.doukaku.org/lang/erlang/">
	  Erlang
	</a>]
	
	
	
	&nbsp;

<span class="rating">評価<span style="background-color: #ffffff;">0/0=0.00</span></span>
  </p>
  <div class="comment_content">
	<div class="comment_body">
	  <p>file_size.erlで保存し、以下のように実行します。:</p>
<pre class="literal-block">
$ erl -noshell -s file_size file_size file_size.erl -s init stop
189
</pre>
<p>存在しないファイル（例えばdummy.txtとする）を指定すると、何も表示されません。:</p>
<pre class="literal-block">
$ erl -noshell -s file_size file_size dummy.txt -s init stop
</pre>

	</div>
	
	
	
    <div class="compact">
      <table><tr><td class="linenos"><pre>1
2
3
4
5
6
7
8</pre></td><td class="code"><div class="highlight"><pre>-module(file_size).
-export([file_size/1]).

file_size(Name) -&gt;
    case filelib:is_file(Name) of
        false -&gt; ok;
        true -&gt; io:format(&quot;~B~n&quot;, [filelib:file_size(Name)])
    end.
</pre></div>
</td></tr></table>
    </div>
	

  
